list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: a circular ornamental headdress worn by a monarch as a symbol of authority, usually made of or decorated with precious metals and jewels.
the top or highest part of something.
the part of a tooth projecting from the gum.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: a thin layer of enamel covers the crown
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: một lớp men mỏng bao phủ vương miện

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: a British coin with a face value of five shillings or 25 pence, now minted only for commemorative purposes.
a paper size, now standardized at 384 × 504 mm.
ceremonially place a crown on the head of (someone) in order to invest them as a monarch.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: he went to Rome to be crowned
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Anh ấy đã đến Rome để được trao vương miện

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: rest on or form the top of.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: the distant knoll was crowned with trees
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Knoll xa xôi đã được trao vương miện với cây

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: be the triumphant culmination of (an effort or endeavor, especially a prolonged one).
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: years of struggle were crowned by a state visit to Paris
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Nhiều năm đấu tranh đã được trao vương miện bởi một chuyến thăm nhà nước đến Paris

list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: simple fillings no longer suffice and the tooth has to be crowned
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Trám đơn đơn giản không còn đủ và răng phải được trao vương miện

list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: she contained the urge to crown him
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Cô ấy khao khát vương miện anh ta

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: (of a baby's head during labor) fully appear in the vaginal opening prior to emerging.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: I was able to see our baby's head crowning
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Tôi đã có thể nhìn thấy vương miện đầu của em bé
